  "imageCount": 11,
  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/91dcc9822e4d5fe3.jpg?v=1782539314\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Any chance I get to take a little trip to <a href=\"http://www.urbanicpaper.com/\">Urbanic</a>, I do a happy dance. This place is a feast for creative gurus and anyone who appreciates good design on a greeting card. Wanna dress up your gift with some cute paper and ribbon? This is the place to go. Wanna have them customize your stationery? Done! I spy a bit of Amy Tangerine product on their shelf! </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"5b-IMG_1242.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/1ec1e19cd6a3c2de.jpg?v=1782539316\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"5c-IMG_1245.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/79f6349744648c3f.jpg?v=1782539319\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"5d-IMG_1246.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/487a29443a273e84.jpg?v=1782539322\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"5e-IMG_1251.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/ac27298bd05eaedb.jpg?v=1782539325\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"5f-IMG_1252.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/e02ab9afdeb3d128.jpg?v=1782539327\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"5g-IMG_1262.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/8e4c352550854bd8.jpg?v=1782539331\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Jack still likes hanging out and going on adventures in <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00BJCFNKU/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B00BJCFNKU&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=wwwamytangeri-20&amp;linkId=CRPHBMMOLNJBZ6AC\">the Ergo</a>. Lucky us - we bumped into the lovely <a href=\"http://www.smittenstudioonline.com/\">Sarah of smitten studio!</a></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"5h-IMG_1264.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/2e3d39ca38e78af5.jpg?v=1782539333\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"5i-IMG_1267.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/844828083aa844ff.jpg?v=1782539336\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"5j-IMG_1269.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/447d4feb60277355.jpg?v=1782539339\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"5k-IMG_1281.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/3b33e60e24131bb0.jpg?v=1782539341\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>And the goodies that made it home with me. I wish I could bring home the entire store! Ahhh, self restraint! Photos by <a href=\"http://jacshootblog.com/\">Jamie Waters</a></p>"
}